oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Honoring Brother I. Leo
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: De La Salle Christian Brothers; Archivists
oai_dc:dc.dc:description:
Brother I. Leo O'Donnell, Christian Brothers College's first archivist, received the Brother Lawrence Egbert Distinguished Service Award at the first annual Alumni Reunion weekend.
Others pictured were (L-R): Tom Fehrmann, Michael Daush, and Brother Theodore Drahmann.
